{
    "text": "Asked the Beast to take a video of me in my new library \ud83d\udc81\u200d\u2640\ud83d\udcda  This \u2018library\u2019 in reality is the beautiful C\u0103rture\u0219ti Carusel bookstore in Bucharest, Romania! \ud83c\uddf7\ud83c\uddf4   Located in the heart of old town, the store provides a quiet bright hideaway in the midst of the city.   It does get quite busy, so if you\u2019re planning a visit I\u2019d recommend heading there as soon as it\u2019s open to explore the massive labyrinth of books in both English and Romanian - they even have a cafe for your morning coffee fix \u2615   Have you ever seen a prettier shop? \u2728   #bucharest #romania #carturesticarusel #bookstagram #everydaymagic #cottagecoreaesthetic #cottagecorefashion #autumngirl #realmsandenchantment #cottagecore #romaniatravel",
